episode.title: Live From WWDC 2015
episode.rawTitle: 123: Live From WWDC 2015 With Guest Phil Schiller
episode.author: Daring Fireball / John Gruber
episode.description: Recorded in front of a live audience at Mezzanine in San Francisco, John Gruber is joined by Phil Schiller to discuss the news from WWDC: OS X 10.11 El Capitan, iOS 9, the new native app SDK for Apple Watch, Apple Music, and the 2004 American League Championship series.
